Description: An institutional-grade quantitative research platform for financial
    analysis, macroeconomic intelligence, statistical modelling, and automated
    reporting. Implements portfolio optimisation, CAPM, ARIMA/GARCH econometrics,
    Monte Carlo simulation, and interactive Shiny dashboards.
